		<title>20LANGUAGE</title>
		<content> The main language used in Glyncorrwg  
 is English only a small minority of   
 people actually speak Welsh fluently. 
 Quite a large number of the older     
 people will use some Welsh words in   
 their conversations but they do not   
 talk solely in Welsh. The Welsh       
 language is taught in the school but  
 no lessons are taught through the     
 medium of Welsh. The young people are 
 not encouraged to use the Welsh       
 language and if present trends        
 continue then the use of Welsh will   
 eventually die out.                   
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
